data.description: Move in ready 3 bedroom home with bonus room and private back yard is waiting for you! You'll be the brick home on the hill. The hardwood floors, amazing stone work on the fireplace, tub, and backsplash, the newly updated kitchen, and new flooring in the home are just some of the amazing features you'll find as you walk in. This home has the master suite on the main level and a powder room for guests. The remaining bedrooms and the bonus room are all upstairs. Great for guests and as a separation from main area living. The back yard is fenced with a nice deck/patio area.  This is one home you'll need to see quickly! Call today to schedule your private showing.
